{"tid":1504780,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥：溝通平台形式必須突破過往","createTime":"2019-08-25T11:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T22:59:53.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":179,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"bdc7bd18a20b70ebb45f0f60aca507ab895186a9","tid":1504780,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:39:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網站回應網民批評，指希望構建的平台是面向全港市民。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥昨日在facebook發表文章後收到數萬個留言，她發文感謝網民留言，無論持甚麼立場都會看和感受網民的留言。對於不少網民批評政府過往的對話不夠全面，質疑今次又是花招、拖延時間，林鄭月娥表示希望構建的平台是面向全港市民，形式必須突破過往的局限，必須與公眾進行直接、深入及持續互動的對話，平台仍在構思和籌備階段，希望能夠盡快推出，歡迎大家在提出意見。"},{"pid":"d5682a93616bababc68624d7d8cfc67fee52ab15","tid":1504780,"uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:39:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360405\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360405&d=6v%2BmLhPCoO19KIzpXGl1DrtFVp6nBI01qSlVibQweWg%3D&h=e174fc56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D360405&h=130053bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=360405</a>"},{"pid":"a6157b5dd8cfe3e855a13802ea4c84aa0366f904","tid":1504780,"uid":212626,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"上連登啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d477b0ed488adbf9968ec6b4b0a89fb21ac7854b","tid":1504780,"uid":122,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"知 用水炮射鳩人同專打頭嘛<br />\n西女人"},{"pid":"44fd787eef740c48e7f2e8cbc0bca31c8b50838d","tid":1504780,"uid":64743,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T11:41:32.000Z","msg":"構佢老母呀<br />\n落地獄啦<br />\n佢究竟知唔知幾多人被捕<br />